      "text": "Because Swiss don't-- send everybody back to France over 16-year-old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They have too many refugees there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we are stuck in Leone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
